{
  "stem": "18102.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they would go to the shops and buy and stand in line to get their food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And the, the street was always bustling, except by Friday night, when things would get-- be very quiet.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "This was the Jewish quarter, and of course Friday night was the beginning of the Sabbath.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And everything quieted down, and all the shops closed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And Saturday it was very, very quiet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Sunday, too, and it didn't start until Monday again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Our room that was rented overlooked this very scene.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I would often stand in front of the little window, which had a little grating where you could step out, actually, onto a veranda, a very small veranda, just enough for one person.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I would, for hours, stand there and watch, in awe, this scene below me, truly mesmerized by what I saw and the people haggling and arguing and buying and selling and-- you know, a scene that, literally, it does not exist anymore, as far as I know, anywhere in the world.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "This was unusual.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Very colorful.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Extremely interesting.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Highly unusual.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I, I, I was just overwhelmed by the scene.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just out of science fiction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It may have given me a little bit of that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, really, truly, a marvel, especially for a young kid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all of a sudden, you know, things were a little bit more normal.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father and mother were around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was, I was enrolled in school-- now first grade.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I met my first real girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her name was Esther, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Her last name was Mann.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- her parents were teachers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my parents knew them from the Vilna seminary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So this was like a reunion for them.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
